title: Arakawa Under The Bridge
alternative_title: 荒川アンダーザブリッジ ; 荒川爆笑团
status: 荒川アンダーザブリッジ ; 荒川爆笑团
description:
Description :
        Gag manga about a young "elite" man who has a policy of not being in debt to anyone. But he ends up owing his life to a strange girl who saves his life. Nino, the girl, believes she is from venus & lives under the bridge by the Arakawa river. So the young man ends up living there too. - - - Ichinomiya Kou has always lived according to the creed of his wealthy, successful family: never be in debt to anyone. But one day, under the Arakawa Bridge, his life is saved by a homeless girl named Nino. In order to pay her back, Kou promises to be her boyfriend; and thus begins his new life under the bridge.
